     Threshold 1 @0x7D67C: rpm 1600,2000,2400,2800,3200,3600,4000 -> 100,100,30,28,25,15,5
     Threshold 2 @0x7D6B4: rpm 2000,2050,2400,2800,3200,3600,4000 -> 100,100,90,50,30,10,0
